132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST REGULAR SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 631
H.P. 399 House of Representatives, February 25, 2025
An Act to Allow a Home Distiller to Distill and Share Homemade
Spirituous Liquor
Received by the Clerk of the House on February 20, 2025. Referred to the Committee on
Veterans and Legal Affairs pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered printed pursuant to Joint
Rule 401.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative SCHMERSAL-BURGESS of Mexico. (BY REQUEST)
Cosponsored by Senator MARTIN of Oxford and
Representatives: BAGSHAW of Windham, HALL of Wilton, HENDERSON of Rumford,
